sys_remote_update_set.description:
This template emphasizes a clean, modern, and neutral design that can be tailored to fit a wide variety of company brands.
Installation instructions: 1. Install the following plugins: Floor Plan Viewer, Facilities Service Automation, Human Resources Service Automation: Core, Human Resources Service Automation: Employee Change, Chat. Include demo data where possible.
2. Upload the included font files (System Definition > Upload File).
3. Load this update set.
To change the portal URL: Go to Content Management > Sites > Branded CMS. Update the URL suffix field.
To change the home page title: Go to Content Management > Pages > Branded CMS. Update the Title field.
To change the footer contents: Go to Content Management > Dynamic > Branded CMS Footer. Update the text.
To change the main logo: Go to Content Management > Headers > Branded CMS Header. Update the Logo field with your own image.
To turn off chat links: Go to Content Management > Navigation Menus > Branded CMS Global Menu. Click on the "Chat By Department" Menu Item. Uncheck the Active field and save.
To change the scrolling banner images: Go to Content Management > Bootstrap Carousels > Branded CMS Home Carousel. Here you can edit or create new slides. Click into any of the carousel slides and edit their content, as well as update the images they may be referencing as their background image. To replace the existing images, go to Content Management > Images, and replace branded-cms-banner-1.jpg, branded-cms-banner-2.jpg, and branded-cms-banner-3.jpg. You can also upload your own images here and reference them in your slides. For optimal viewing, please use an image that is at least 1140 pixels wide and 500 pixels tall.
Tested in Chrome, Firefox, Safari, and IE9+

For a nice way to experiment with colors, see https://color.adobe.com/create/color-wheel/. An even simpler color picker can be found at http://colorpicker.com/.
*********/

/* General Link Styles */
a {
	color: #D1232B;
	transition: color 200ms;
}
a:hover { /* When the mouse is hovering over a link */
	color: #A61C23;
	text-decoration: none; /* removes underlines when hovering */
}
a:active, a:focus { /* When the mouse is in the middle of a click or just after a link has been clicked */
	color: #A61C23;
	text-decoration: underline;
}

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="content_css"><content_css action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><name>Branded CMS Layout Styles (Mobile)</name><style>/* Mobile + Default Styles */

.page-title, .branded-admin-nav, #page_timing_div { display: none; }

.cms_header { padding-bottom: 40px; }

.cms_header_top_menu .cms_menu_super_menu_content { display: none; }
td.cms_header_top_menu { height: 40px; padding-bottom: 20px; line-height: 40px; }

.cms_header span.globalSearch { display: block; margin-top: 5px; line-height: 20px; }
.cms_header span.globalSearch #sysparm_search { margin-left: 5px; width: 100%; }
.cms_header_login_link { text-align: right; }

.cms_header_resizer_link:last-child { margin-left: 10px; }

td.cms_header_logo, td.cms_header_text { display: block; }
div.cms_header_text,
.cms_header_bottom_menu { display: none; }

.cms_header_text .cms_menu_super_menu_bar_item,
.cms_header_text .cms_menu_super_menu_bar_item_selected { float: left; }
/*.cms_header_text .cms_menu_super_menu_bar_item a,
.cms_header_text .cms_menu_super_menu_bar_item_selected a {  }*/
.cms_header_text .cms_menu_super_menu_bar .menu_section {
	display: block;
	padding: 0 15px;
	font-size: 18px;
	letter-spacing: 0.05em;
	line-height: 1.5;
	text-transform: uppercase;
}
.cms_header_text .cms_menu_super_menu_content { display: none; }

/* Home Page */
.main-content .carousel { display: none; }

.main-content .cms_menu_section_blocks .cms_menu_section_blocks_image_left { width: 90px; }
.main-content .cms_menu_section_blocks .cms_menu_section_blocks_title { padding-left: 20px; }
.page-home .main-content .cms_menu_section_blocks .cms_menu_section_blocks_title { padding-left: 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid #999; }
.main-content .cms_menu_section_blocks .cms_menu_section_blocks_title h2 {
	margin: 0;
	font-size: 22px;
	font-weight: 400;
	letter-spacing: 0.05em;
}
.main-content .cms_menu_section_blocks .cms_menu_second_level_text { letter-spacing: 0.05em; font-size: 12px; }
.main-content .cms_menu_section_blocks .cms_menu_separator { display: none; }
.main-content .cms_menu_section_blocks .main-content-menu-block-items { padding: 20px 0 40px 100px; }
.main-content .cms_menu_section_blocks .main-content-menu-block-items td { padding-bottom: 10px; }
.main-content .cms_menu_section_blocks .main-content-menu-block-items tr:last-child td { padding-bottom: 0; }
.main-content .cms_menu_section_blocks .menu_bullet { min-width: 20px; }
.main-content .cms_menu_section_blocks .cms_menu_block_item {
	display: block;
	margin-left: 10px;
	font-size: 18px;
}

/* Home Pages */
.main-content .cms_menu_vertical_block .cms_menu_vertical_blocks_image_left { width: 90px; }
.main-content .cms_menu_vertical_block td.cms_menu_vertical_blocks_title { padding-left: 20px; }
.main-content .cms_menu_vertical_block .cms_menu_vertical_blocks_title h2 {
	margin: 0;
	font-size: 22px;
	font-weight: 400;
	letter-spacing: 0.05em;
	text-transform: uppercase;
}

/* Iframe pages */
.branded-page-title {
	margin: 0 0 20px;
	font-size: 24px;
	letter-spacing: 0.05em;
	line-height: 1;
	text-transform: uppercase;
}
#catalog_frame, #support_frame { margin-top: 40px; }

/* Support Pages */
.page-it_support .main-content .cms_menu_section_blocks .cms_menu_section_blocks_title h2,
.page-hr_support .main-content .cms_menu_section_blocks .cms_menu_section_blocks_title h2,
.page-facilities_support .main-content .cms_menu_section_blocks .cms_menu_section_blocks_title h2 { font-size: 18px; }
.page-it_support .main-content .cms_menu_section_blocks .cms_menu_section_blocks_image_left,
.page-hr_support .main-content .cms_menu_section_blocks .cms_menu_section_blocks_image_left,
.page-facilities_support .main-content .cms_menu_section_blocks .cms_menu_section_blocks_image_left { width: 60px; }

/* knowledge styles */
.kb-list-article { margin-bottom: 20px; }
.kb-list-article-views,
.kb-list-article-votes { text-align: center; }
.kb-list-article-views.not-viewed,
.kb-list-article-votes.not-useful { color: #999; }
.kb-list-article-views.viewed { color: inherit; }
.kb-list-article-views.viewed .kb-list-article-views-content { border-color: #333; }
.kb-list-article-votes.useful { color: #7ac143; }
.kb-list-article-votes.useful .kb-list-article-votes-content { border-color: #7ac143; }
.kb-list-article-views-content,
.kb-list-article-votes-content { padding: 15px 0; border: 1px solid #f1f1f1; }
.kb-list-article-views-value,
.kb-list-article-votes-value { font-weight: bold; }
.kb-list-article-text div:empty { display: none; }
.kb-list-article-short-description { margin: 0; font-size: 16px; }
.kb-list-article-description {
	overflow: hidden;
	margin: 5px 0;
	text-overflow: ellipsis;
	white-space: nowrap;
}
.kb-list-article-meta { color: #999; font-size: 12px; }
.kb-list-article-author-name { font-weight: bold; }

/* Footer */
.branded-footer {
	margin-top: 40px;
	padding-top: 20px;
	padding-bottom: 20px;
	font-size: 12px;
	font-weight: 500;
	letter-spacing: 0.05em;
	text-transform: uppercase;
	border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
}
.branded-footer-left,
.branded-footer-right { text-align: center; }
</style><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2014-11-21 08:55:40</sys_created_on><sys_id>152c224d4de8310062c55dc1f2a64e72</sys_id><sys_mod_count>89</sys_mod_count><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2014-12-05 20:56:16</sys_updated_on><type>local</type><url/></content_css><sys_app_file action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><customer_update>false</customer_update><publish_override/><replace_on_upgrade>false</replace_on_upgrade><restore/><sys_app/><sys_code>!!K,N/</sys_code><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2014-11-21 08:55:40</sys_created_on><sys_id>d3344f119b30310018621c760654982f</sys_id><sys_mod_count>0</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Branded CMS Layout Styles (Mobile)</sys_name><sys_parent/><sys_path>!!K,N/</sys_path><sys_policy/><sys_source_deleted>false</sys_source_deleted><sys_source_id>152c224d4de8310062c55dc1f2a64e72</sys_source_id><sys_source_table>content_css</sys_source_table><sys_type/><sys_update_name>content_css_152c224d4de8310062c55dc1f2a64e72</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2014-12-05 20:56:16</sys_updated_on></sys_app_file></record_update>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="content_css"><content_css action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><name>Bootstrap Overrides</name><style>/* Concessions made to Bootstrap Styles because of ServiceNow's layout engine. */

/* Fade Carousel */
.carousel .carousel-inner .item { display: block; opacity: 0; transition: opacity 1.5s; }
.carousel .carousel-inner .active { opacity: 1; }
.carousel .carousel-inner .left,
.carousel .carousel-inner .right { left: 0; }
.carousel .carousel-inner > .item.prev,
.carousel .carousel-inner > .item.active.left { transform: none; -webkit-transform: none; }

/* Margins for columns have to be changed for table cells (margins don't affect them) */
td.row > table > thead > tr > th[class*="col-"]:first-child,
td.row > table > tbody > tr > td[class*="col-"]:first-child,
td.row > div[class*="col-"]:first-child {
	padding-left: 0;
}

td.row > table > thead > tr > th[class*="col-"]:last-child,
td.row > table > tbody > tr > td[class*="col-"]:last-child,
td.row > div[class*="col-"]:last-child {
	padding-right: 0;
}
</style><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2014-11-23 02:25:43</sys_created_on><sys_id>b985af214dec310062c55dc1f2a64e86</sys_id><sys_mod_count>12</sys_mod_count><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2014-12-05 20:34:10</sys_updated_on><type>local</type><url/></content_css><sys_app_file action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><customer_update>false</customer_update><publish_override/><replace_on_upgrade>false</replace_on_upgrade><restore/><sys_app/><sys_code>!!K,R/</sys_code><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2014-11-23 02:25:43</sys_created_on><sys_id>d7344f119b30310018621c7606549832</sys_id><sys_mod_count>0</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Bootstrap Overrides</sys_name><sys_parent/><sys_path>!!K,R/</sys_path><sys_policy/><sys_source_deleted>false</sys_source_deleted><sys_source_id>b985af214dec310062c55dc1f2a64e86</sys_source_id><sys_source_table>content_css</sys_source_table><sys_type/><sys_update_name>content_css_b985af214dec310062c55dc1f2a64e86</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2014-12-05 20:34:10</sys_updated_on></sys_app_file></record_update>

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_ui_script"><sys_ui_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><description>Adding bootstrap classes and updating the layout for the Branded CMS Template.</description><global>false</global><name>branded-cms-layout</name><script><![CDATA[jQuery.noConflict();

( function( $j ) {
	var applyBrandedStyles = function() {
			var $headerLogoContainer = $j( 'td.cms_header_logo' );

			$j( 'html' ).attr( 'data-doctype', false ).data( 'doctype', false );

			// setting up top menu
			$j( 'td.cms_header_top_menu' ).addClass( 'row' );

			// $j( 'div.cms_header_search, div.cms_header_top_menu' ).addClass( 'col-xs-12' );
			// $j( '.cms_header_font_size, .cms_header_login' ).addClass( 'col-xs-6' );

			// $j( 'div.cms_header_search' ).addClass( 'col-md-2' );
			// $j( '.cms_header_font_size' ).addClass( 'col-md-1' );
			// $j( '.cms_header_login' ).addClass( 'col-md-4' );
			// $j( 'div.cms_header_top_menu' ).addClass( 'col-md-5' );
			$j( 'div.cms_header_top_menu' ).addClass( 'hidden-xs' );

			// setting up logo row
			$j( '.cms_header_logo_row > td' ).addClass( 'row' );
			$j( 'td.cms_header_logo' ).addClass( 'col-xs-6 col-md-2' );
			$j( 'td.cms_header_text' ).first().addClass( 'branded-main-menu-container col-xs-6 col-md-10' );
			$j( '.cms_header_bottom_menu' ).children().appendTo( '.branded-main-menu-container' );

			// setting up horizontal block menus
			$j( '.main-content .cms_menu_section_blocks' ).each( function( i, el ) {
				var $menuBlock = $j( el ),
					$menuBlockParent = $menuBlock.parent(),
					numBlocksPerRow = 1,
					columnsPerRow = 12,
					columnsPerBlock;

				if ( !$menuBlockParent.hasClass( 'row' ) ) {
					$menuBlockParent.addClass( 'row' );
				}

				numBlocksPerRow += $menuBlock.siblings().length;
				columnsPerBlock = Math.floor( columnsPerRow / numBlocksPerRow );

				$menuBlock.addClass( 'col-xs-12 col-md-' + columnsPerBlock );
			} );

			$j( '.main-content .cms_menu_section_blocks > table > tbody > tr:nth-child(2) > td' ).addClass( 'main-content-menu-block-items' );
		},

		hideAdminBar = function() {
			$j( '.branded-admin-nav' ).hide();
		};

	$j( document ).ready( function() {
		// testing if the page elements have loaded. If so, immediately apply styles. Otherwise, wait a second. This is mainly to offset the extra latency involved when editing a page.
		if ( $j( 'td.cms_header_logo' ).length ) {
			applyBrandedStyles();
		} else {
			setTimeout( function() { applyBrandedStyles(); hideAdminBar(); }, 400 );
		}

		// overriding default submenu offset function
		getOffset = function( item, attr ) {
			var parentElement = getFormContentParent(),
				wb = 0;

			if ( item ) {
				wb += item[ attr ];
			}

			return wb;
		};
	} );

} )( jQuery );
]]></script><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2014-11-21 10:17:52</sys_created_on><sys_id>aeceb6cd4de8310062c55dc1f2a64e87</sys_id><sys_mod_count>16</sys_mod_count><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2014-12-04 23:53:57</sys_updated_on></sys_ui_script><sys_app_file action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><customer_update>false</customer_update><publish_override/><replace_on_upgrade>false</replace_on_upgrade><restore/><sys_app/><sys_code>!!K.J/</sys_code><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2014-11-21 10:17:52</sys_created_on><sys_id>d2444f119b30310018621c76065498f9</sys_id><sys_mod_count>0</sys_mod_count><sys_name>branded-cms-layout</sys_name><sys_parent/><sys_path>!!K.J/</sys_path><sys_policy/><sys_source_deleted>false</sys_source_deleted><sys_source_id>aeceb6cd4de8310062c55dc1f2a64e87</sys_source_id><sys_source_table>sys_ui_script</sys_source_table><sys_type>code</sys_type><sys_update_name>sys_ui_script_aeceb6cd4de8310062c55dc1f2a64e87</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2014-12-04 23:53:57</sys_updated_on></sys_app_file></record_update>

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="content_css"><content_css action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><name>Branded CMS Layout Styles (Small Screens)</name><style>@media ( min-width: 768px ) {
	div.cms_header_search, .cms_header_font_size, .cms_header_login, div.cms_header_top_menu { float: right; padding: 0 15px; text-align: center; }

	div.cms_header_top_menu,
	td.cms_header_text { position: relative !important; }
	.cms_header_top_menu .cms_menu_super_menu_content,
	.cms_header_text .cms_menu_super_menu_content {
		position: absolute;
		padding: 10px 15px;
		text-align: left;
		background: #fff;
		border: 1px solid #666;
		z-index: 1;
	}
	.cms_header_text .cms_menu_section_blocks_title h2,
	.branded-chat-link {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: 16px;
		font-weight: 400;
		letter-spacing: 0.05em;
		line-height: 1.5;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		vertical-align: middle;
	}

	.cms_header_top_menu .cms_menu_section_blocks_title h2 { display: none; }
	.cms_header_top_menu .cms_menu_super_menu_content { min-width: 300px; }
	.branded-icon-chat { margin-right: 10px; }

	.main-content .carousel { display: block; margin-bottom: 40px; }
	.main-content .carousel-inner,
	.main-content .carousel-inner > .item { height: 310px; }
	.main-content .carousel-inner > .item { position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; }
	.main-content .carousel-control,
	.main-content .carousel-indicators { display: none; }
	.main-content .carousel-caption { left: 10%; right: 10%; text-shadow: 0 0px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); }
	.main-content .carousel-caption h3 {
		font-weight: 500;

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="content_css"><content_css action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><name>Branded CMS ServiceNow Overrides</name><style>/* Overriding default CMS/Iframed styles */

table, input, select, button, input.text, textarea, input.button {
	font-size: inherit;
	font-family: inherit;
}

/* Iframed forms and lists */
html[data-doctype=true] body[data-formName="ui_page_render"] { margin: 0; }
html[data-doctype=true] div.section_header_content_no_scroll { overflow: visible; }
div.form_title { font-size: 14px; }
.label { display: block; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; }
.label label { margin-bottom: 0; }

.breadcrumb { padding: 0; background: transparent; }

/* Service Catalog */
#category_description, #navigatordetailTop { display: none; }

.sc_category_item .details_div td,
.sc_category_item_hover .details_div td,
.catalog_description > table > tbody > tr > td { padding: 10px; }
.sc_category_item .details_div h3:first-child,
.sc_category_item_hover .details_div h3:first-child,
.catalog_description > table > tbody > tr > td > h3:first-child { margin-top: 0; }

/* Catalog Shopping Cart Container */
#cartContent { padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ccc; }
.sc_cat_set_window, .sc_cart_window { margin: 0; border: 0 none; }
.sc_cart_window { min-width: 175px; width: 100% !important; }


/* Catalog Shopping Cart Top */
#cartContent_header { padding-bottom: 10px; }
#cart { padding: 0 10px; border: 0 none; }
#adder { border: 1px solid #CCC; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 10px; }
#qty { margin-top: 10px; }

/* Catalog Shopping Cart Bottom */
.sc_cart_subtotal_row td { padding-top: 10px; }

/* Live Feed */
.main-content .live_feed_column { padding: 0; }</style><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2014-11-24 17:14:12</sys_created_on><sys_id>d7fafb024da0710062c55dc1f2a64ee3</sys_id><sys_mod_count>16</sys_mod_count><sys_updated_by>kai.yao</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2014-12-02 22:57:58</sys_updated_on><type>local</type><url/></content_css><sys_app_file action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><customer_update>true</customer_update><publish_override/><replace_on_upgrade>false</replace_on_upgrade><restore/><sys_app/><sys_code>!!M|]/</sys_code><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2014-11-24 17:14:12</sys_created_on><sys_id>21a8c5b0b134310062c560307f6433b5</sys_id><sys_mod_count>0</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Branded CMS ServiceNow Overrides</sys_name><sys_parent/><sys_path>!!M|]/</sys_path><sys_policy/><sys_source_deleted>false</sys_source_deleted><sys_source_id>d7fafb024da0710062c55dc1f2a64ee3</sys_source_id><sys_source_table>content_css</sys_source_table><sys_type/><sys_update_name>content_css_d7fafb024da0710062c55dc1f2a64ee3</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>kai.yao</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2014-12-02 22:57:58</sys_updated_on></sys_app_file></record_update>
